      • timeout

        @Nullable
TimeValue timeout()
        The timeout for this cluster state update task configuration. If the cluster state update task isn't processed within this timeout, the associated ClusterStateTaskListener.onFailure(String, Throwable) is invoked.
        Returns:
        the timeout, or null if one is not set
